imdb.plot outline: Jo Frost steps into the homes of several families in various parts of the US. Recognising and resolving the broken relationships and communication within the family unit. Using her 25 years of experience she helps the families to reconnect, respect, love and support one another, creating a happy home environment and more importantly a happy family!
